# RuangTato.com — Tattoo Studio Directory Marketplace

## Quick Reference
- **Stack**: Next.js 16 / Drizzle ORM / PostgreSQL / Better Auth / Tailwind v4
- **Aliases**: `@/` → `src/`
- **UI Library**: shadcn/ui (base-nova) from `@/components/ui/`
- **Icons**: lucide-react
- **Payments**: Midtrans

## Rules
Detailed rules are in `.cursor/rules/` — this file just loads them:
- `00-global.mdc` — Stack, TypeScript, imports
- `01-ui-ux.mdc` — Tailwind, spacing, responsive
- `02-design-system.mdc` — shadcn/ui, icons, typography
- `03-database.mdc` — Drizzle ORM, schema, queries
- `04-api-routes.mdc` — Route handlers, auth, Midtrans
- `05-copywriting.mdc` — Tone, glossary, conversion copy
